headline: Memecoins: Anyone's Guess As To What Will Happen Next, But It Feels Like It's Going To Be Wild
summary: Nothing stops the launch of many more meme coins; we are leaving the Fartcoin stage and entering the Trump (and Melania) memecoin stage. What will happen next?
